    "We analyzed how Facebook users want the recommendations to be explained.",
    "This section contains the answers to the first part of RQ, which depicts explanation attributes that end users need.",
    "Users are concerned about how Facebook uses their data to provide recommendations.",
    "They think that these platforms utilize usage history to provide them with recommendations.",
    "Users also have abstract ideas regarding data sharing among various third-party applications."
